{"tid":421827,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國槍襲] 極端組織伊斯蘭國（IS）承認責任","createTime":"2017-10-02T14:31:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T16:01:19.000Z","uid":119979,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"90bd23f5cdfc56dcc2499bd3dd99cd6573e6e2b5","tid":421827,"uid":119979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:31:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20171002/57281599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20171002%2F57281599&d=UuZ1iPTJC%2FYJcpizRsrAQGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=7d62945d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20171002%2F57281599&h=7d06fc86\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20171002/57281599</a><br />\n<br />\n美國拉斯維加斯有槍手在酒店房向一個戶外音樂會的觀眾亂槍掃射，迄今造成逾50死，當地醫院共接收了逾400名傷者。槍手在房內有至少十支槍，他在警方抵達前自盡，並相信他並無同黨。以下是最新進展：<br />\n<br />\n● 槍手是64歲白人帕多克（Stephen Paddock），據稱是「當地居民」，槍手在上周四已入住酒店<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">● 極端組織伊斯蘭國（IS）承認責任，稱槍手幾個月前已經改信伊斯蘭教，但沒有提供證據</span><br />\n● 槍手擁有打獵和捕魚許可證，並有機師執照，他在內華達州沒有無案底<br />\n● 警方尋獲曾與疑兇同行的亞裔女性<br />\n● 美國總統特朗普向死者致哀<br />\n● 槍手是在32樓酒店房間中，用自動步槍向戶外音樂會的觀眾亂槍掃射，他至少擁有十支槍<br />\n● 初步相信屬「孤狼」襲擊，不屬任何武裝組織<br />\n● 死者中有兩人是休班警員<br />\n<br />\n指事發在周日晚，槍手在曼德勒海灣賭場度假村附近一個音樂會開槍。網傳片段可見有人爭相走避，另一段在高處拍攝的影片亦見到大群民眾突然散開逃走，而且傳來半自動步槍的槍聲，一名女士叫道：「我的天，快伏下、伏下。」<br />\n<br />\n疑犯為64歲男子帕多克（Stephen Paddock），是土生土長的拉斯維加斯市民，無跡象顯示與恐怖組織有連繫，相信是單獨施襲，動機未明，「完全不理解他持甚麼心態」。警方搜查疑犯的住所和兩輛汽車，並尋到曾與他同房的62歲亞裔女伴丹妮（Marilou Danley）。<br />\n拉斯維加斯音樂會槍擊案已成為美國史上最血腥槍擊案，超越去年6月12日釀成49死58傷的奧蘭多同性戀夜總會恐襲。"},{"pid":"6e6161b0f2d9ce710ea546a8d49e68dc85c62bd1","tid":421827,"uid":119979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce5305aa68b03f79f9d8a81d618dbdbf86364b5","tid":421827,"uid":35763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:33:22.000Z","msg":"正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f617271100afd8beae2eed9d489870662cbad11","tid":421827,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:34:01.000Z","msg":"繼續咩都唔做由D癲佬買槍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731e70300e212bb42c01a474b5de4a83ff748af2","tid":421827,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:34:39.000Z","msg":"trump trump 幾時種族清洗班 IS"},{"pid":"916ac556cdeee4b2e3685a2e3aa837b6668e2e0b","tid":421827,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcae3b7cceae290c978e8303fe9c094090f23d94","tid":421827,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:35:16.000Z","msg":"9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94f9298b255f9c5c37c2a995fc0d874e0b133d3","tid":421827,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:35:40.000Z","msg":"槍手：關你撚事咩"},{"pid":"96b33de43eaf6833615198cc3975422eecbf2523","tid":421827,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:37:54.000Z","msg":"沒有證據.jpg"},{"pid":"57431d09e2c8143694f24ee5f6ba543e773b39be","tid":421827,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:38:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d74d4db046170a4a0995c88901540a488575a19f","tid":421827,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:39:38.000Z","msg":"係唔係都承認責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9eecdd1f7de2767511431bad1296f73464dbd9","tid":421827,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:39:40.000Z","msg":"一句allahu akbar都無都幾難信係isis"},{"pid":"0200b